  m_text: '17. Palpate umbilical cord to check pulsation

    18. Clamp the cord
    using clamp or cord tie, 2cm from the base

    19. Place the instrument clamp
    5 cm from the base or 3 cm from the plastic clamp

    20. Cut the cord near
    the plastic clamp (close to the first clamp, not midway)

    21.  Deliver the
    placenta

    22. Perform hand hygiene and don clean gloves



'
